snippet: Lindsey Vonn, a four-time overall World Cup champion, needed stitches in her thumb after trying to break up a fight between her dogs over a Frisbee.
abstract: Champion skier Lindsey Vonn requires stitches on her thumb after breaking up fight between her dogs.
